snippet.textDisplay: Kanishk and Kavish 🫡 highly talented individuals. I had the good fortune of spending some of my childhood with them. We were in the same school. snippet.textDisplay:
This song took me back to the childhood memory when my mom used to sing for me and my brother at night. My mom used to sing “dhire se aaja re akhiyan me.. neendiya aaja re aaja.. chup ke se aaja”. Her voice was so beautiful. I am not exaggerating but exactly like shreya ghosal. 

She regrets that she couldn’t record her song back in those time. Otherwise she might have sung for any movie.
